methods.doMainFound:
Called after a value is found in the main hash table

:param tableLocation: (int) - location in the table
:param chunkPosition: (int) - the position in the chunk
methods.doMainInsert:
Called after a value is inserted into the main hash table

:param tableLocation: (int) - location of insertion
:param chunkPosition: (int) - the position in the chunk
methods.doMissing:
Called during probe when a value is not found in main or overflow.

:param chunkPosition: (int) - the position in the chunk
methods.doMoveMain:
Called during rehash when a value is moved in the main table

:param oldTableLocation: (int) - the old location in the main table
:param newTableLocation: (int) - the new location in the main table
methods.doOverflowFound:
Called after a value is found in the overflow hash table

:param overflowLocation: (int) - location in the overflow table
:param chunkPosition: (int) - the position in the chunk
methods.doOverflowInsert:
Called after a value is inserted into the overflow hash table

:param overflowLocation: (int) - location of insertion
:param chunkPosition: (int) - the position in the chunk
methods.doPromoteOverflow:
Called during rehash when a value is promoted from overflow to the main table

:param overflowLocation: (int) - the old location in the overflow table
:param mainInsertLocation: (int) - the new location in the main table
methods.onNextChunk:
Called when the next chunk of data is being processed in build or probe.

:param size: (int) - the size of the next chunk
